summary: Very simple little mod that lets you craft some of the unique and unenchantable vanilla jewelry.
descriptionHtml: I was always annoyed that all the cool looking jewelry was pre enchanted and unique so i made this little mod to \"fix\" that.You can now craft unenchanted versions of all the religious amulets.   Akatosh, Dibella, Zenithar, Mara, Stendarr, Kynareth, Julianos, Arkay, Talos. You can also make the Ancient Nord Amulet, The Necromancer Amulet, The Elder Council Amulet And Wolf Ring which uses hircines ring mesh.
author: Chillwill
